## Accessibility Requirements

### ARIA and IDs

```html
<!-- Labelled by -->
<div role="dialog" aria-labelledby="modal-title" id="settings-modal">
  <h2 id="modal-title">Settings</h2>
</div>

<!-- Described by -->
<input id="password-input" 
       type="password"
       aria-describedby="password-requirements">
<div id="password-requirements">
  Must be at least 8 characters
</div>

<!-- Controls -->
<button aria-controls="user-menu-dropdown" 
        aria-expanded="false"
        id="user-menu-toggle-button">
  Menu
</button>
<div id="user-menu-dropdown" class="hidden">
  <!-- Menu items -->
</div>
```

### Form Accessibility

```html
<!-- Always associate labels with inputs -->
<label for="user-email-input">Email Address</label>
<input id="user-email-input" 
       type="email"
       aria-required="true"
       aria-invalid="false">

<!-- Error messages -->
<input id="user-password-input" 
       type="password"
       aria-describedby="password-error"
       aria-invalid="true">
<div id="password-error" role="alert">
  Password is required
</div>
```
